<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <style>
      body {
        /* background-color: black; */
        font-family:Georgia, 'Times New Roman', Times, serif;
      }

      li,
      h4,
      p {
        color: #323256;
      }

      h4 {
        font-weight: 700;
        font-size: 14px;
      }

      p {
        font-weight: 400;
        font-size: 14px;
        line-height: 22px;
      }

      .flex-container {
        height: 100%;
        width: 100%;
      }

      .letter-document {
        width: 100%;
        height: auto;
        text-align: center;
        /* border: solid red; */
      }

      .flex-container,
      .letter-header,
      .letter-footer {
        text-align: center;
        margin: 10px 0;
      }

      .letter-header,
      .letter-footer {
        letter-spacing: 1px;
        width: 100%;
        color: #c4c5c5;
        background-color: #f8f8ff;
      }

      .letter-header {
        padding: 20px 0;
        font-size: 15px;
        font-weight: 900;
        text-transform: capitalize;
        border-bottom: solid 1px #d4d9db;
      }

      .letter-footer {
        font-size: 12px;
        font-weight: 300;
        padding: 45px 0;
        border-top: solid 1px #d4d9db;
      }

      .content-letter {
        height: auto;
        width: 400px;
        margin: auto;
        text-align: left;
        /* border: solid green; */
        padding: 16px 15px;
        box-sizing: border-box;
      }

      .content-letter h4 {
        text-transform: capitalize;
      }

      .content-letter .user {
        text-transform: capitalize;
      }

      #button-section {
        width: 100%;
        padding: 30px 0;
        margin: 10px 0;
        /* border: solid yellow; */
        background-color: #f8f8ff;
        text-align: center;
      }

      #button-section button {
        outline: none;
        cursor: pointer;
        border: solid 1px #8a8abaab;
        padding: 10.5px 37px;
        margin: 10px 0;
        background: transparent;
        color: #8A8ABA;
        font-size: 15px;
        font-weight: 600;
        border-radius: 3px;
        text-transform: capitalize;
      }

      #button-section button:active {
        background-color: rgb(214, 79, 162);
        color: #f8f8ff;
      }

      .plan-details {
        /* border: solid red; */
        margin-left: -15px !important;
      }

      .plan-details ol > li {
        font-weight: 600;
        font-size: 14px;
      }

      .plan-details ul > li {
        font-size: 14px;
      }


    </style>
    <title>Welcome</title>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="letter-header">
      <h3>skyview trading</h3>
    </div>
    <div class="flex-container">
      <div class="centered">
        <div class="letter-document">
          <div class="content-letter">
            <h4>hi there!</h4>
            <p>
              Welcome <span class="user"><%= client.name %></span>, thank you so much for choosing us
              by signing up to our platform.
            </p>
            <p>
              We appreciate your confidence in us and we are pleased to offer you our quality services. Your
              satisfaction is our priority
            </p>
            <p>
              Your success starts with skyview trading providing you with a signup bonus of $50 accompined 
              with the best possible customer support. That is why our 24/7 support team is staffed by real people
              who are passionate about helping you get the most out of this platform.
            </p>
            <p>
              Kindly click on the login below to get redirected back to our server so as to start your investment 
              with any plan of your choice.
            </p>
            <div id="button-section">
              <a href="https://skyviewtrading.co.uk/login"><button>login</button></a>
            </div>
            <p>
              If you did not create an account, no further action is required.
            </p>
            <br />
            <p>Regards,
              <br>
              Skyview trading
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="letter-footer">
      <span>&copy; skyview trading. All rights reserved.</span>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
